Package: gglm
Type: Package
Title: Easy diagnostic {ggplot}s for generalized linear models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
  person("Grayson", "White", email = "graysonwhite13@gmail.com", role = c("cre","aut")))
Description: This is an R package that allows for easy creation of `ggplot` diagonostic plots. 
  This package was inspired by the base R functionality of `plot()` with objects of class `glm` and `lm`.
